{"tid":1876475,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【黃色經濟諗吓計？］唔敢去玩 有Party Room生意額大跌八成","createTime":"2020-02-12T12:00:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T15:00:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"003ba35a5c7a230b3b5258bdfd8799a7c57f403c","tid":1876475,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:00:42.000Z","msg":"【Now財經台】早前有大型家庭群組，於派對場地吃火鍋後，感染新型冠狀病毒。有派對場地負責人表示，事件發生後即時有客人改期及取消預訂。<br />\n<br />\n近年興起租用派對場地，即是Party Room玩樂消遣，不過早前有大型家庭群組，於一間派對場地內吃火鍋和燒烤後，集體感染新型冠狀病毒的個案，引起不少人對租用場地的憂慮。<br />\n<br />\nTim跟拍檔，於旺角、荔枝角及尖沙咀經營派對場地。他表示事件發生後，有70%客人改期或取消預訂，現時亦不讓客人在場地吃火鍋。<br />\n<br />\n他表示肺炎疫情爆發後，近一個月生意額大跌約80%，並認為疫情對生意的影響，較去年社會運動大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W32JXOV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW32JXOV.png&h=240245a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HzHej2A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHzHej2A.png&h=eeb10a49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTim表示自上月初，內地爆發肺炎疫情後，場地已經加強消毒，亦有聘請清潔公司，每日到場清潔及消毒。負責人指，為了減低病毒傳播的機會，他們會準備酒精搓手液予客人，一些玩樂設備如遊戲機，他們也會用清潔劑消毒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/564905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fmobile%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F564905&d=DYxn%2BwEapY32uLV96Ej4GARUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=4b8dc0ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/mobile/news/article/564905</a><br />\n<br />\n好大隻連豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nParty room 可以點轉型"},{"pid":"498114e45009e0991da921dc0851f8631f20e927","tid":1876475,"uid":269148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:06:37.000Z","msg":"做隔離所"},{"pid":"da78fa9e6bc75342d6b292fcec4f47adcfa7a668","tid":1876475,"uid":168522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:49:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個時勢真係好艱難"},{"pid":"4c2097176a61bbc435d1fca8b931b8bdd18fc509","tid":1876475,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"498114e45009e0991da921dc0851f8631f20e927","tid":1876475,"uid":269148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T12:06:37.000Z","msg":"做隔離所"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T13:36:42.000Z","msg":"要睇政府頭<br />\n<br />\n或者轉做網店貨倉？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4a6ad334c7c264a1ad40296c5ce35cb8d9c71e","tid":1876475,"uid":6297,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T14:41:57.000Z","msg":"跟住香港政府地政總署按網上party room 廣告，去晒每一間喺工廠大廈改做party room 嘅場地告佢業主改地契用途，連個20%都唔俾直接執笠"},{"pid":"8ac3901e789359f4dfe6eaa2e10fa297d927a8ac","tid":1876475,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T15:00:58.000Z","msg":"呢個時勢<br />\n起碼等半年先有人敢去"}]}